      <title>董事会终止收购谈判后梅西百货债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/macy-s-bonds-slide-after-board-terminates-buyout-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅西百货公司 (Macy’s Inc.) 债券周一早盘下跌，此前该公司表示，将终止与 Arkhouse Management Co. 和 Brigade Capital Management 就收购该百货连锁店的潜在谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/macy-s-bonds-slide-after-board-terminates-buyout-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:15:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>针对低评级 CLO 的 ETF 规模首次超过 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一只购买低评级担保贷款债务（CLO）敞口的交易所交易基金的资产规模已超过 10 亿美元，这对于曾经仅对机构投资者开放的市场中快速增长的 CLO 基金而言又是一个里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论谁担任总统，税收都会增加，市政债券因此更具吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/tax-hikes-seen-no-matter-who-s-president-making-case-for-munis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MacKay Shields LLC 表示，无论谁赢得 11 月的美国总统大选，美国人明年都将缴纳更高的税款。这使得市政债券成为一种有吸引力的保护伞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/tax-hikes-seen-no-matter-who-s-president-making-case-for-munis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
